sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Usuario
    participant UI
    participant BE as API + Runtime
    participant FS as Firestore
    User->>UI: Abrir chamado
    UI->>BE: POST /runtime/requests
    BE->>FS: tx read workflowType + version + counter
    BE->>FS: tx create workflows/{docId}
    BE-->>UI: requestId, status=open
    UI->>BE: POST /requests/{id}/assign
    BE->>FS: update responsible + status=in_progress
    BE-->>UI: responsavel definido
    UI->>BE: POST /requests/{id}/request-action
    BE->>FS: append actionRequests + status=waiting_action
    BE-->>UI: aguardando resposta de terceiro
    User->>UI: Responder acao pendente
    UI->>BE: POST /requests/{id}/respond-action
    BE->>FS: update actionRequests + recalc statusCategory
    BE-->>UI: controle volta ao usuario responsavel
    UI->>BE: POST /requests/{id}/advance ou /finalize
    BE->>FS: update stepStates + currentStepId + fechamento quando aplicavel
    BE-->>UI: status=in_progress ou finalized
    UI->>BE: POST /requests/{id}/archive
    BE->>FS: set isArchived=true + status=archived
    BE-->>UI: item arquivado
